                <h1>Understanding Dark Social: The Hidden Sharing Phenomenon</h1>
                <p>Dark social refers to the sharing of content that occurs through private channels like messaging apps, email, and direct messaging on social networks. Unlike traditional social media shares that are easily trackable, dark social remains largely invisible to marketers, making it a challenge to measure its impact on traffic and engagement.</p>
